criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adults at least 18 yrs who are hospitalized and initiated on IV vancomycin

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  renal instability

          -  immunosuppression;

          -  vancomycin allergy;

          -  history of recurrent peritonitis

          -  administration of < 4 doses of vancomycin

          -  pregnancy;

          -  hemoglobin < 8 g/dL.
